Description:
    "Creates all necessary .js, .scss and .vue files to implement a simple CRUD using Vue-Router"

Example:
    rails generate vue_app CloudHouse::Company::Employee

    This will create:
        /engines/CloudHouse/app/vue/company_employees/app.js
        /engines/CloudHouse/app/vue/company_employees/apps/list.vue
        /engines/CloudHouse/app/vue/company_employees/apps/new.vue
        /engines/CloudHouse/app/vue/company_employees/apps/show.vue
        /engines/CloudHouse/app/vue/company_employees/apps/edit.vue
        /engines/CloudHouse/app/views/cloud_house/company/employees.index.html.erb
        /engines/CloudHouse/app/views/cloud_house/company/employees.new.html.erb
        /engines/CloudHouse/app/views/cloud_house/company/employees.show.html.erb
        /engines/CloudHouse/app/views/cloud_house/company/employees.edit.html.erb
        /engines/CloudHouse/app/assets/stylesheets/cloud_house/company/employees.scss

    rails generate vue_app Core::Role

    This will create:
        /app/vue/roles/app.js
        /app/vue/roles/apps/list.vue
        /app/vue/roles/apps/new.vue
        /app/vue/roles/apps/show.vue
        /app/vue/roles/apps/edit.vue
        /app/views/roles/index.html.erb
        /app/views/roles/index.new.erb
        /app/views/roles/index.show.erb
        /app/views/roles/index.edit.erb
        /app/assets/stylesheets/roles.scss
